reviews.review_text: To~To, I Don't Think We're In Kansas Anymore ? The Banter In Thru The Start Os Set I Says It All. They Came To Play. And Make Some Music Too. Wondrous Music To Finish Up An Amazing Two Part Fall And LATE Fall Tour. Thank You Charlie. All The Best.
